snippet.title: Nusantara: Bermuda Triangle - Teaser
snippet.description:
PC game（Windows/Mac/Linux）English

Nusantara: Bermuda Triangle is an epic fantasy adventure with a strong spice of romance, mystery, and Indonesian flavour. 

If you like this video, please consider checking out our IndieGoGo and try the demo : https://igg.me/at/BermudaVN
